Layer.ows:Title: Base of Hooray Sandstone and Equivalents
Layer.ows:Abstract: Base of Hooray Sandstone and equivalents surface, elevation values in mAHD. This surface is identified as "Layer 05" in the set of twelve surfaces of geological formations containing major aquifers and aquitards in the Great Artesian Basin produced for the Great Artesian Water Resource Assessment (GABWRA) by Geoscience Australia, a three-dimensional visualisation product that accompanies "The three-dimensional visualisation of the Great Artesian Basin" report (Nelson et al., 2012).
